org.openscience.smsd.algorithm.vflib

Class MCSSeedGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openscience.smsd.algorithm.vflib.MCSSeedGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Callable<List<AtomAtomMapping>>

    public class MCSSeedGenerator
extends Object
implements Callable<List<AtomAtomMapping>>
    This class should be used to find MCS between source graph and target graph. First the algorithm runs VF lib VF2MCS and reports MCS between run source and target graphs. Then these solutions are extended using McGregor McGregor algorithm where ever required.
    Author:
    Syed Asad Rahman
